    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-review-board",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The CFD model predicts NIH within ±12% of in-vitro measurements across 4 of 5 COU operating points, and RH < 1 is confirmed at the worst-case predicted condition. The exclusion of viscoelastic blood rheology from the model is documented in the model form factor rationale and is considered of low impact based on the high-shear impeller environment. The credibility assessment team accepts the evidence package as sufficient to support the 510(k) hemolysis submission claim.",
